reviewText: I grew up on THE PRESUADERS, CHAMPIONS, THE AVENGERS (with Steed and Mrs. Peel), and THE PRISONER. ABSOLUTELY LOVE this era doe TV entertainment. Beats the hell out of what they're making today.

Auctionade is a trickster. They really knew my order (The persuaders - 13 episodes on 4 DVD's) and they sent me a cheap movie (Stay- 1 DVD) instead. So, first I have to send back the movie with the cost it takes, in order to get the movie series I requested.
Where is the customer service?
